Building
To build the project use following command:
.


Running
After building the application run following command to start it:

e.g. `java -jar target/homework-app.jar -Ddatasource=misc/books.json`


Access
Endpoints available at the url:

- Book by ISBN url: /api/book/{isbn}
- Book by category url: /api/category/{categoryName}/books
- Author rating url: /api/rating